Package: wrathos-bundle-gpu
Version: 1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: WrathOS Project <zxd@lunarys.org>
Depends: wrathos-base
Description: WrathOS GPU drivers bundle
 Installs GPU drivers appropriate for your hardware.
 Includes AMD, NVIDIA, and Intel driver support along
 with Vulkan ICD loaders for all vendors.
